# Committed smoke-test video fixtures (small, deliberately un-ignored so CI can
# exercise the real ffmpeg pipeline against them; must come after every *.mp4/
# *.mkv rule above so the negation isn't re-shadowed).
!test/smoke_test_videos/*.mp4
!test/smoke_test_videos/*.mkv
docs/
.superpowers/
